This is a combat map in the middle of space. I garantee you can play this map for hours. There are many cool features and you never gets tired of it.
I worked my ass off to make this map. I appriciate you not editing the map, or do anything about it, without my permission.

This map is designed for normal surf, training your surf skills, tcombat surf, Deathmatch, RPG and can be used for much much more

The map is very stylish and has some very sniper spots. And there are loads of fun features.

Enjoy! I made this for you!
